Help On The Way-> Slipknot!-> Franklin's Tower-> Women Are Smarter, He's Gone-> Drums-> Truckin'-> Black Peter-> Not Fade Away, E: Revolution

reviews.review_text:
Great 83' show Haven't heard all that much from this era, I tend to stay in the 60's-70's but this is a solid energetic show containing some great jams that really pack a punch...better than the Dick's Picks 10/14 release IMO. Definitely worth a full listen, they're smokin' by the 2nd half of the first set & it just keeps getting better.

Good sound on this matrix.
5 stars for 83'
4 stars overall
1983 Jerry so filthy in every sense Outstanding show!!! Barely remember being there.. Dusbourne Matrix is pure gold.. 5 stars show and sound quality
